                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def4-693-18610819 t18610819-693-punishment-53"></join>
                     <hi rend="italic">and they were discharged on their own recognizances to appear and receive judgment if called upon.</hi>
                  </rs>
               </p>
